org.lobobrowser.html.w3c

Interface HTMLTextAreaElement

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.w3c.dom.Element, HTMLElement, org.w3c.dom.Node
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    HTMLTextAreaElementImpl

    public interface HTMLTextAreaElement
extends HTMLElement
    Multi-line text field. See the TEXTAREA element definition in HTML 4.01.

    See also the Object Model (DOM) Level 2 HTML Specification

    .
